      "role": "user",
      "content": "a \"goblin in the shadows\" clause? i'm not sure i follow. can you explain what you mean by that? it sounds like you're saying there are sneaky ways for these liabilities to pop up even if i haven't done anything wrong.",
      "source": "evaluator"
